    skos:inScheme dpvs:core ;
    skos:note """The exact definition of what constitutes "scale" depends on use of
jurisdictional, domain-specific, or other forms of externally defined
criteria. Where possible, this should be reflected by extending the
scales provided with the appropriate context.""" ;
